### get my profile
GET http://localhost:8000/api/user/profile

### update my profile (text only)
PUT http://localhost:8000/api/user/profile
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Updated Name",
    "phone": "9999999999"
}

### create a listing (use REST Client file upload for images)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/user/listings
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="title"

Sony WH-1000XM3
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="description"

Used for 3 months, works perfectly
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="price"

3500
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="category"

Electronics
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="condition"

Like New
--boundary--

### get my listings (all)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/user/listings

### get my active listings
GET http://localhost:8000/api/user/listings?status=active

### get my sold listings
GET http://localhost:8000/api/user/listings?status=sold

### get my expired listings
GET http://localhost:8000/api/user/listings?status=expired

### edit a listing — replace id with real one
PUT http://localhost:8000/api/user/listings/LISTING_ID_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "Updated Title",
    "price": 3000
}

### mark listing as sold — replace id with real one
PUT http://localhost:8000/api/user/listings/LISTING_ID_HERE/sold

### renew listing — replace id with real one
PUT http://localhost:8000/api/user/listings/LISTING_ID_HERE/renew

### delete a listing — replace id with real one
DELETE http://localhost:8000/api/user/listings/LISTING_ID_HERE

### logout
POST http://localhost:8000/api/user/logout